6fg4eeagae64g080d5cdbc969": ["Yet we thrive. It is <i>madness.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "fafc3e80-a734-ec3e-f653-a4c80a22081c"], "hfd76c5e0gd1d8g4377gac23gb7726b547f5c": ["On the <i>gh'ath</i> - the ship. There was a voice. It promised to <i>change</i> us.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "c3961cf0-0071-d548-e569-cc845ae5d82d"], "hd7f67a52g32e4g4093gb105gf5ffeb25e6b8": ["Yes. I heard it too.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "e11e0188-4b00-0d01-18aa-a93d6a086143"], "hbf6469dfga955g49a1g8ccfg3114910f2918": ["The voice, the promise - they are manipulations. They are obscene. <i>Reject them.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "63f9598e-8432-d9f7-414e-f1c067204ec2"], "he2e4f4fbgc749g40a2gb5b8g944985c3154d": ["You speak true. Purification must be our first priority.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "56dc69e4-e527-0676-d2d3-11195a234a01"], "h546b9bd7g82fbg4af9g89dfgec181b6d8671": ["Indeed. Finding a cure is all that matters.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "56dc69e4-e527-0676-d2d3-11195a234a01"], "h0898e5beg8142g4abagbd39gd265690ecb1b": ["Wise words. I am almost impressed.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "dc0429a7-f91d-dbee-d607-ddb252754310"], "hb5bf5492gf0d6g4693g982fg657ee8ed58f7": ["The voice offers power. Vlaakith would not have us refuse it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night2_CRD_Laezel.html", "a4c745db-